Class CimMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.aifusion.metamodel.QualifiedElement
      • net.aifusion.metamodel.CimMethod
  • public class CimMethod
extends QualifiedElement
    Class to represent a CIM Method. CIM Methods are created as part of CIM Class definitions by the MOFParser.

    Sharad Singhal
